knowing my mom

01:42:39.786 --> 01:42:41.547
and I've never met her before,
but she approached me.

01:42:41.549 --> 01:42:42.836
She consoled me.

01:42:42.838 --> 01:42:45.045
She told me about this séance,
and she showed me how.

